import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

function Header() {
  return (
    <Navbar expand="lg" className="bg-body-tertiary">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand href="#home">React-Bootstrap</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="me-auto">
            <Link className='nav-link' to="/">Home</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="add-group">Add Group</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="add-library">Add Library</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="add-message">Add Message</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="add-contact">Add Contact</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="pagenotfound">Pagenotfound</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class1">Cls1</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class2">Cls2</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class3">Cls3</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class4">Cls4</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class5">Cls5</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class6">Cls6</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class7">Cls7</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class8">Cls8</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class9">Cls9</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class10">Cls10</Link>
            <Link className='nav-link' to="Class11">Cls11</Link>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Header;
